1992 Repeal.

Chapter 65 (Subchapters A - G) was added November 15, 1972, P.L.1063, No.271, and repealed December 14, 1992, P.L.835, No.134, effective in 60 days. The subject matter is now contained in Article XXIV of the act of May 17, 1921, P.L.682, No.284, known as The Insurance Company Law of 1921.
